snippet.title: Skwish for Playdate - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
https://pawprints.games/skwish-playdate

Tidy blocks and solve brainteasers in this satisfying puzzle game for the Playdate console! Free demo includes the first twelve levels.

Trailer made by  @TinyYellowMachine .
